rows.label: tlk44500188_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I'm on a break. I deserve
it - I've been working
solidly through lunchtime.

rows.label: tlk44500188_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I wonder what'll happen
now that we've got a steady
influx of outlanders?

rows.label: tlk44500188_02_msg0003
rows.name:
That's just what a youngster like you
would say. Bringing in the new isn't
necessarily always a good thing...

rows.label: tlk44500188_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Now, what's to become of Luxuria? Will
it live on for generations to come? Or
will it wither and die before I do...?
